00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:24,000
Û milyon qet kirin û pir xelk mera biştaxilîn û naskirin ko
em Efrînî ne.
 
And it crossed millions and many people interacted with us
and realized we are from Afrin.

118
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:27,000
