You say your fame is by coincidence.

119
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:30,000
Şans e. Şans e. Û hinek teeb jî gerek e.
 
It's luck. It's luck. And some effort is needed too.

120
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:34,000
