Do you have your own original songs under your name? Do you
have your own songs, music videos under your name?

123
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:47,000
Bi xwedê min hinek tumar kirine, yanî ji peyvên xwe û ji
awaza...
 
By God, I have recorded some, I mean from my own words and
melodies...

124
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:50,000
Lê ema hîn dest min neketiye ez tiştî çêbikim.
 
But I haven't had the chance to produce anything yet.

125
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:55,000
Bi rastî birayê min Memcan, ez cara yekem e, min tu li ser
